title: Rosy Beef and Zucchini Penne with Roasted Pepper Pesto
description: Short on time but longing for a delicious dinner? This pasta recipe is here to the rescue! Flavour bombs like roasted pepper pesto and grated Parmesan cheese do the heavy lifting to amp this blush sauce, while spinach and grated zucchini bring veggie wholesomeness.
